50 void move_group::MoveGroupCapability::convertToMsg(const std::vector<plan_execution::ExecutableTrajectory>& trajectory,
51  moveit_msgs::RobotState& first_state_msg,
52  std::vector<moveit_msgs::RobotTrajectory>& trajectory_msg) const
53 {
54  if (!trajectory.empty())
55  {
56  bool first = true;
57  trajectory_msg.resize(trajectory.size());
58  for (std::size_t i = 0; i < trajectory.size(); ++i)
59  {
60  if (trajectory[i].trajectory_)
61  {
62  if (first && !trajectory[i].trajectory_->empty())
63  {
64  moveit::core::robotStateToRobotStateMsg(trajectory[i].trajectory_->getFirstWayPoint(), first_state_msg);
65  first = false;
66  }
67  trajectory[i].trajectory_->getRobotTrajectoryMsg(trajectory_msg[i]);
68  }
69  }
70  }
71 }

73 void move_group::MoveGroupCapability::convertToMsg(const robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectoryPtr& trajectory,
74  moveit_msgs::RobotState& first_state_msg,
75  moveit_msgs::RobotTrajectory& trajectory_msg) const
76 {
77  if (trajectory && !trajectory->empty())
78  {
79  moveit::core::robotStateToRobotStateMsg(trajectory->getFirstWayPoint(), first_state_msg);
80  trajectory->getRobotTrajectoryMsg(trajectory_msg);
81  }
82 }

84 void move_group::MoveGroupCapability::convertToMsg(const std::vector<plan_execution::ExecutableTrajectory>& trajectory,
85  moveit_msgs::RobotState& first_state_msg,
86  moveit_msgs::RobotTrajectory& trajectory_msg) const
87 {
88  if (trajectory.size() > 1)
89  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Internal logic error: trajectory component ignored. !!! THIS IS A SERIOUS ERROR !!!");
90  if (!trajectory.empty())
91  convertToMsg(trajectory[0].trajectory_, first_state_msg, trajectory_msg);
92 }

94 planning_interface::MotionPlanRequest
95 move_group::MoveGroupCapability::clearRequestStartState(const planning_interface::MotionPlanRequest& request) const
96 {
97  planning_interface::MotionPlanRequest r = request;
98  r.start_state = moveit_msgs::RobotState();

116 std::string move_group::MoveGroupCapability::getActionResultString(const moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes& error_code,
117  bool planned_trajectory_empty, bool plan_only)
118 {
119  if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::SUCCESS)
120  {
121  if (planned_trajectory_empty)
122  return "Requested path and goal constraints are already met.";
123  else
124  {
125  if (plan_only)
126  return "Motion plan was computed succesfully.";
127  else
128  return "Solution was found and executed.";
129  }
130  }
131  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::INVALID_GROUP_NAME)
132  return "Must specify group in motion plan request";
133  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::PLANNING_FAILED ||
134  error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::INVALID_MOTION_PLAN)
135  {
136  if (planned_trajectory_empty)
137  return "No motion plan found. No execution attempted.";
138  else
139  return "Motion plan was found but it seems to be invalid (possibly due to postprocessing). Not executing.";
140  }
141  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::UNABLE_TO_AQUIRE_SENSOR_DATA)
142  return "Motion plan was found but it seems to be too costly and looking around did not help.";
143  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::MOTION_PLAN_INVALIDATED_BY_ENVIRONMENT_CHANGE)
144  return "Solution found but the environment changed during execution and the path was aborted";
145  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::CONTROL_FAILED)
146  return "Solution found but controller failed during execution";
147  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::TIMED_OUT)
148  return "Timeout reached";
149  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::PREEMPTED)
150  return "Preempted";
151  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::INVALID_GOAL_CONSTRAINTS)
152  return "Invalid goal constraints";
153  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::INVALID_OBJECT_NAME)
154  return "Invalid object name";
155  else if (error_code.val == moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::FAILURE)
156  return "Catastrophic failure";
157  return "Unknown event";
158 }

177 bool move_group::MoveGroupCapability::performTransform(geometry_msgs::PoseStamped& pose_msg,
178  const std::string& target_frame) const
179 {
180  if (!context_ || !context_->planning_scene_monitor_->getTFClient())
181  return false;
182  if (pose_msg.header.frame_id == target_frame)
183  return true;
184  if (pose_msg.header.frame_id.empty())
185  {
186  pose_msg.header.frame_id = target_frame;
187  return true;
188  }
189 
190  try
191  {
192  geometry_msgs::TransformStamped common_tf = context_->planning_scene_monitor_->getTFClient()->lookupTransform(
193  pose_msg.header.frame_id, target_frame, ros::Time(0.0));
194  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped pose_msg_in(pose_msg);
195  pose_msg_in.header.stamp = common_tf.header.stamp;
196  context_->planning_scene_monitor_->getTFClient()->transform(pose_msg_in, pose_msg, target_frame);
197  }
198  catch (tf2::TransformException& ex)
199  {
200  ROS_ERROR("TF Problem: %s", ex.what());
201  return false;
202  }
203  return true;
204 }

206 planning_pipeline::PlanningPipelinePtr
207 move_group::MoveGroupCapability::resolvePlanningPipeline(const std::string& pipeline_id) const
208 {
209  if (pipeline_id.empty())
210  {
211  // Without specified planning pipeline we use the default
212  return context_->planning_pipeline_;
213  }
214  else
215  {
216  // Attempt to get the planning pipeline for the specified identifier
217  try
218  {
219  auto pipeline = context_->moveit_cpp_->getPlanningPipelines().at(pipeline_id);
220  ROS_INFO_NAMED(getName(), "Using planning pipeline '%s'", pipeline_id.c_str());
221  return pipeline;
222  }
223  catch (const std::out_of_range&)
224  {
225  ROS_WARN_NAMED(getName(), "Couldn't find requested planning pipeline '%s'", pipeline_id.c_str());
226  }
227  }
228 
229  return planning_pipeline::PlanningPipelinePtr();
230 }
